name: IBUonline
overview: As the unique global one-stop & two-way B2B marketplace, IBU is designed and published by Shenzhen IBU Co., Ltd, which formerly named as Hotnewnet Trading Co., Ltd and has been engaged in international trade for almost 10 years and served thousands of enterprises in the field of FPC, LED, Electronics, Building Material and Home Furnishing etc, always devoted to offer superior qualified and effective foreign trade services for companies throughout the world. IBU is more than an international business platform; we not only connect global buyers and suppliers, but also participate in the whole process of international trade, provide a series of practical services (off the platform) to greatly enhance the efficiency of global trade. Working with us, you can benefit from the real one-stop service for the first time
